[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "本劇情涉及主線劇情第11章與活動劇情「矛盾之心‧瑪利昂」的核心內容。", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0055.wav"], "content": "鎖定……開火！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0055.wav"], "content": "唔喝啊啊啊！這下就結束啦！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "作戰完畢。我軍損耗非常輕微。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "嘿嘿。這點程度的敵人，只要有我跟艾零出馬根本是小意思！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1017.wav"], "content": "她們真的很厲害呢……──畢竟由1000年前的技術製造，性能高是當然的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "1000年前的戰鬥人偶嗎……記得那個時代，文明超發達的對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1011.wav"], "content": "──是的。我們是仿照那個時代的戰鬥人偶而被製造出來的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "──但是，她們和我們製造時代的基礎技術不同。所以，並無法達到完全重現。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "──是啊。在基本性能上，艾零她們比我們要來得優秀許多。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "真的假的……以後可能還會有那樣的傢伙來攻擊我們對吧？記得是叫艾克斯‧馬奇那？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是啊……不過同樣身為戰鬥人偶，如果能避免彼此爭鬥是最好的了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "但很遺憾，那不可能。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1042.wav"], "content": "艾零……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "1000年前，有極少數的人類建造了空中都市方舟，並藉此從地上逃離。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "他們認為地上已被龍族奪去，遺留在地上的人類，都是投靠龍族的背叛者。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我們艾克斯‧馬奇那，則是為了成為方舟上僅存人類的雙手與劍而建立的組織。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "艾克斯‧馬奇那將現在活動於地上的都視為敵人。從1000年前就一直沒變。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100006_story/VO_CHR_100006_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "所以說已經持續戰鬥1000年了嗎……待在那個「方舟」裡的傢伙們，應該早就世代交替了說。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100006_01.png", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "是啊。當初組織艾克斯‧馬奇那的人大概都已經不在了吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "可是，來自方舟的命令卻沒有改變。所以，艾克斯‧馬奇那……總司令的瑪契娜不會停止戰鬥。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "不過，我倒是爽快多了。她老是滿嘴命令命令，一下必須做這個一下不准做那個的，超煩的啊～", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……的確，不管什麼時候離開都不奇怪呢。畢竟我已經沒有身為艾克斯‧馬奇那戰鬥的理由。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0046.wav"], "content": "所以，我真的覺得是你們給了我們很好的契機。請讓我再次道謝。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1019.wav"], "content": "別這樣，道謝什麼的……夥伴變多我們也很高興啊。──是。妳們很可靠。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "你們也替我修好了「心」，真是幫了大忙啊。如果繼續失控下去，事情就不妙了呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1033.wav"], "content": "──啊、不……菲霓的「心」並沒有修好。因為「心」有太多無法解析的部分……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我們只修好了由於外殼破損導致內部跑出來的地方而已。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "──耐衝擊性應該有提升。但是，無法解決根本上的問題。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "難怪……我之前還在想，連艾克斯‧馬奇那的技術都無法修理的「心」，你們是怎麼修好的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（如果是這樣，代表菲霓的「心」就還處於損壞的狀態……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（如果，發生什麼意外……也有可能會再次失控……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "拉契希、馬斯科拉……我有事想問你們……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "當拉契希的「心」因損壞而失控時，馬斯科拉將自己的「心」給了她對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "意思是你們兩人，原本就具備那種機能嗎……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1033.wav"], "content": "咦？不、不是的……我們並沒有那種機能。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只是想說我和拉契希機型相同，所以覺得應該能用我的「心」，去代替拉契希壞掉的「心」。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "也就是說……你當時並不確定嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1014.wav"], "content": "呃、是啊……──馬斯科拉，就是這樣。經常，走一步算一步。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1061.wav"], "content": "──當時我只是拼了命地想阻止拉契希……卻沒想到「心」會混合在一起。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "那果然是預料外的結果啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（說得也是……交換「心」之後，記憶和人格並不會留下，這點我已經證實過了……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1058.wav"], "content": "艾零……該不會，妳打算將自己的「心」給菲霓嗎……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_0061.wav"], "content": "──反對。我們是特殊例子。無法期待「心」的混合。妳自身消失的可能性很高。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "我當然並非在期待發生「心」混合的奇蹟。只要菲霓能恢復原狀，那就夠了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "菲霓在1000年間一直待在我身邊，是無可替代的搭檔。如果能修好菲霓的心，無論要付出任何代價……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──艾零……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "如果給出我的「心」能夠讓菲霓復原，我願意。不過，只有這樣是不夠的。沒辦法讓她恢復原狀。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "所以，我才想參考你們這對成功的例子。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "──恐怕無法參考。我和馬斯科拉機型相同。設計上即使交換零件也能100％運作。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "推斷也是因此就算交換「心」，彼此的「心」也能成功運作。妳和菲霓是否可能？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "……我們當然有相容性，但要說是否能100％運作，就傷腦筋了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1011.wav"], "content": "──是啊。所以，還是避免強行移植「心」比較……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "……原來如此。我知道了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1024.wav"], "content": "呼……太好了。妳願意放棄了吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "相反地，只要吻合度夠高，就還有可能性對吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1006.wav"], "content": "咦！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_05.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "我所謂的「知道了」，是指接下來應該採取的行動方針。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只要確認我和菲霓兩人進行互換的精密度就可以了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只要從艾克斯‧馬奇那的據點，拿到我和菲霓的設計圖……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110384011, "title": "技術問題"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1006.wav"], "content": "妳打算潛入艾克斯‧馬奇那的據點嗎，艾零……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_06.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "沒有問題。我已經為此進行過作戰模擬了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只要沒有不確定因素，成功率能達到90％……這個數值足以進行實踐。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1082.wav"], "content": "我們也跟她去吧，拉契希。考慮到要是有什麼萬一，戰力多一點應該比較好。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_06.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不，這次的作戰由我自己去。雖然很抱歉，但你們反而會成為不確定因素的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100032_story/VO_CHR_100032_STORY_1042.wav"], "content": "咦？什麼意思？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100032_06.png", "speakerName": "拉契希", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "意思是有些事正因我身為艾克斯‧馬奇那的戰鬥人偶才能辦到。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "抵達作戰準備地點。目標對象在……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "……看來是被一起廢棄到郊外了呢。然後，狀態……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0060.wav"], "content": "……不行。破損得太嚴重了。這樣無法使用……其他的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "嗯……這個毀損得更嚴重……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "保有原形的人偶很少呢。還能動的人偶應該都歸隊了，這也是沒辦法的嗎……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "可是……只要仔細找，至少找得到一具能用來進行作戰的人偶吧……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "……！有了！如果是這點程度的損傷……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "對不起。我要暫時借用你的外殼零件了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……任務第一階段，達成。接下來，就是帶著這些零件……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "抵達據點附近。任務第二階段……開始。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "脫去本機的強化臂腕。換裝外殼零件。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "各部位確認……正常。行動沒有問題。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……但這次的作戰，「行動沒有問題」反而會成為問題……所以……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "嗚……！狀態、黃色警戒。腕部及腳部發生損傷……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這下一切準備就緒了。據點潛入……開始！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……歸隊，完畢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120151_story/VO_CHR_120151_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "損傷，確認。前往整備。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "戰鬥人偶", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0029.wav"], "content": "……了解。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……整備完畢。到目前為止都與模擬內容一致，相當順利。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（接下來就是任務最終階段。目標是整備區域內的資料庫……！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（那裡面有整備時必要的情報……也就是我們戰鬥人偶的設計圖！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（連接開始……！好了，讓我看看我和菲霓的設計圖吧……！！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110384012, "title": "戰術指令"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "（找到了……！是指揮官機和量產機的設計圖！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（只要讀取並分析它，就能判斷是否可以將我的心給菲霓……！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（雖然我很想立刻進行分析……但還是以獲得檔案為優先吧。在這裡久留太危險了。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（設計圖檔案傳送，開始……20％……35％……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120218_story/VO_CHR_120218_STORY_0086.wav"], "content": "來自人類解放委員會的通知。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "瑪契娜", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……！！艾克斯‧馬奇那的總司令……瑪契娜！？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120218_story/VO_CHR_120218_STORY_0075.wav"], "content": "確認主要據點附近出現龍族反應。請可行動個體換裝為對龍兵裝後，前往地點246。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "瑪契娜", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120151_story/VO_CHR_120151_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "了解。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_02.png", "speakerName": "戰鬥人偶們", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（怎麼會這樣……！竟然在這個時候下達出擊命令！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（如果我不跟著出擊會遭到懷疑……但設計圖的檔案傳送還沒結束……！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120218_story/VO_CHR_120218_STORY_0082.wav"], "content": "……整備完畢的個體。請進行出擊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "瑪契娜", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（唔……得爭取時間才行……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "……腳部關節發現異常。請求重新整備。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（趁現在將設計圖……！檔案傳送進度，70％……80％……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120218_story/VO_CHR_120218_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "若是輕微異常，要求進行作戰。掃描該個體，確認異常程度。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "瑪契娜", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "未發現腳部關節異常……以及……這是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "瑪契娜", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120218_story/VO_CHR_120218_STORY_0074.wav"], "content": "外殼零件與內部構造不符。該個體為指揮官機……判明為個體名艾零。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "瑪契娜", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "唔！偽裝被看穿了！？不過……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "設計圖的檔案傳送進度……100％！總之達成目的了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120218_story/VO_CHR_120218_STORY_0076.wav"], "content": "排除異常狀況。通告全員。殲滅目標由龍族進行變更。請破壞叛離機艾零。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "瑪契娜", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120151_story/VO_CHR_120151_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "命令收到。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_02.png", "speakerName": "戰鬥人偶們", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "戰鬥模擬，開始……作戰目的為逃出據點……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "確保逃出路徑……移動開始。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120218_story/VO_CHR_120218_STORY_0082.wav"], "content": "命令全員。請追擊個體名艾零。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "瑪契娜", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "抵達中間地點。換裝……開始！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "強化臂腕安裝。回路連接。各部位，沒有異常。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120151_story/VO_CHR_120151_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "艾零，發現。戰鬥，開始。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_02.png", "speakerName": "戰鬥人偶們", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0076.wav"], "content": "雖然我並不想和同是戰鬥人偶的你們戰鬥……但只能應戰了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0055.wav"], "content": "目標，鎖定……開火！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……戰鬥結束。這下追來的人偶就全部……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0057.wav"], "content": "……感應器感知多數反應。看來從據點接連有人偶出擊呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "話雖如此，距離此處還相當遠……能夠順利逃離警戒區域的可能性很高。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "感應器啟動。以最大範圍，偵察開始。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "……好。拉大與追蹤機的距離了。應該能順利逃脫。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "被瑪契娜看穿的時候，還擔心不知道會變怎麼樣……如此一來就能安心了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "接下來，只要分析我和菲霓的設計圖檔案……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "內部機構基礎設計……分析完畢。控制中樞機能設計……分析完畢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "指揮官機與量產機相容性相關設計……分析完畢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0060.wav"], "content": "……結論。要將我的心給菲霓──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120151_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110384013, "title": "替身迷彩"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "要將我的心給菲霓──設計上……不可能……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "怎麼會……那麼，我該怎樣修好菲霓的心……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雖然目前在緊急處置後已經穩定下來，但那孩子的心，一定瀕臨極限了……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "如果、下次又發生了什麼事，一定會失控……不，不只如此……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "有可能心會完全損壞……導致菲霓的意識消失……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "1000年間、一直待在我身邊的菲霓，會消失不見……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………我不要……這種事……我受不了……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120151_story/VO_CHR_120151_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "目標個體捕捉。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "戰鬥人偶", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0044.wav"], "content": "──！？被包圍了！？他們明明已經如此接近，我卻完全沒感知到……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "看來我使用太多系統資源去分析設計圖了呢……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120151_story/VO_CHR_120151_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "瑪契娜的命令收到。叛離機，艾零，排除。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "戰鬥人偶們", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "唔……敵人數量太多了！看來很難強行突破……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這下糟了……戰鬥拖得越久，就會被從據點前來追擊的人偶們追上，遭到夾擊……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0057.wav"], "content": "感應器有反應！後方有敵人！！果然被追上了……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "完全被包圍了……最糟的情況呢。不曉得還有沒有成功回到聖城的可能性……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0048.wav"], "content": "……對不起，菲霓……在妳的心完全損壞之前，我可能會先活動停止了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120151_story/VO_CHR_120151_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "目標個體，排除。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "戰鬥人偶們", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "──！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0055.wav"], "content": "喔喔喔啊啊啊啊！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "艾零！妳沒事吧！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "菲霓！嗯，我沒事……！可是，妳怎麼會在這裡？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那個我等一下解釋！現在得先打倒他們！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你們這些傢伙，竟敢把艾零……！覺悟吧！喔啊啊啊啊！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "已確認敵機殲滅。戰鬥，結束了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "嘿嘿！知道我們兩人聯手的厲害了吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "幸好有妳趕來幫我。不過，妳怎麼會來這裡……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "……我從拉契希那聽說作戰的事之後，就急忙追著妳來了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雖然我覺得艾零擬定的作戰一定不會有問題……但還是擔心……結果發現據點周圍發生騷動……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "原來是這樣……對不起，讓妳擔心了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雖然達成了拿到設計圖的目的，卻不小心被瑪契娜發現……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……不對喔，艾零。我希望妳道歉的，不是這件事。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為什麼艾零想把自己的心給我呢……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0061.wav"], "content": "因為……我想修好妳的心……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "要是那麼做的話，艾零就會像馬斯科拉一樣活動停止了吧！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就算艾零犧牲自己修好我的心……我也完全高興不起來！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "1000年間一直待在我身邊的艾零會消失不見……！！這種事我受不了……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……！！菲霓……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（就像我不想失去菲霓一樣，原來妳對我也……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0048.wav"], "content": "對不起……我從沒考慮過，當我活動停止後，獨自被留下的菲霓會有什麼感受。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "……妳知道就好。不過，妳想犧牲自己的念頭，不可以再有了喔？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我們當中不管剩下誰，都只會感到寂寞……活動停止的時候，要兩個人一起！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "好。我跟妳約定，菲霓。活動停止時，要兩個人一起……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "嗯！我們約好了！艾、零………………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0039.wav"], "content": "……怎麼了？菲霓……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "……喀喀。艾、艾艾、艾零、保護。保護、保護保護──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "菲霓！？妳的心……該不會，因為剛才和戰鬥人偶的戰鬥而……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "艾零的敵人、殲滅、殲滅──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "啊啊……！？住手，菲霓！！妳認不出我了嗎……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "艾零的敵人、殲滅、殲滅──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "怎麼會……難道是心完全損壞，造成失控了嗎……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我不要……求求妳……恢復原狀吧……菲霓……菲霓──！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110384014, "title": "自我犧牲"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "艾零的敵人、殲滅、殲滅──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "唔……菲霓……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（她已經完全失控了……我現在也沒有強制停止的權限，沒有確實能拯救菲霓的方法……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……即使如此……要我放棄，我辦不到！！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0054.wav"], "content": "拜託妳！恢復原狀吧，菲霓！！我們約定過的不是嗎！？約好壞掉之時也要一起……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "約、定……約定……兩個人、一起……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "菲霓！妳聽見我的聲音了……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗚、嗚嗚……活動、停止……不可以……艾零……保護……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "失控停止了一下子……！菲霓的心，還沒完全損壞！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "既然如此……那我就連接到她「心」的深處，直接呼喚她！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我已經藉由設計圖的檔案，分析過控制中樞機能的構造。所以能突破反入侵防禦牆進行連接！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "連接……開始！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "連接成功……這裡就是菲霓的「心」中……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "咦……？艾零……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0021.wav"], "content": "菲霓！太好了……！妳果然還擁有意識！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0086.wav"], "content": "……我已經……不行了。艾零……把我破壞掉吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "什麼……！？妳在胡說什麼，菲霓！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0061.wav"], "content": "……我的存在意義，就是為了艾零而戰。要保護、支持艾零……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但是，我卻……攻擊了艾零！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這種「心」有所損壞的危險人偶，根本沒有資格待在艾零身邊……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我無法、原諒我自己……！所以拜託妳！破壞我吧，艾零……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "……我拒絕。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0037.wav"], "content": "怎麼會……！？為什麼！？這樣下去，我只會傷害艾零……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0041.wav"], "content": "那又如何？比起失去妳，之後必須孤獨地活著，這根本不是問題。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「我們當中不管剩下誰，　都只會感到寂寞……」這些話不是妳說的嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "可、可是……！我、已經……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而且……妳的存在意義，並不在於保護、支持我。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "咦……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只要，待在我身邊……這樣就足夠了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那個約定，菲霓也還記得對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0061.wav"], "content": "…………真的……真的可以嗎？這樣的我……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "我需要妳。需要這1000年間，總是待在我身邊的妳……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0083.wav"], "content": "來，握住我的手。以後，無論發生什麼事……都不要再放開囉……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "艾零……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "菲霓……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0046.wav"], "content": "……謝謝妳，艾零。我要重新和妳約定一次。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "好的。我也和妳約定。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「我們要永遠在一起。　無論壞掉之前，還是壞掉之時。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "艾零＆菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110383_story/VO_CHR_110383_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "我能感覺到……艾零的心，離我非常近……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "我也是……彷彿我們的心，逐漸合為一體似的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就這樣，菲霓的失控順利平息。但菲霓的「心」，卻仍處於損壞的狀態。說實話，我並不知道究竟是什麼阻止了她的失控。", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雖然也曾想過可能是由於我與菲霓雙方的「心」同步所致，但現在那些理論都已經無所謂了。菲霓得救了，這個結果就是一切……", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "對我而言，這就夠了──", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嘿嘿，這樣子，總覺得很安心呢。艾零。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110383_01.png", "speakerName": "菲霓", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110384_story/VO_CHR_110384_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "是啊，我也是，菲霓。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "未來……也要永遠在一起喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110384_01.png", "speakerName": "艾零", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110384015, "title": "雙驅之心"}]